Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  那家伙突然就生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日  你也不玩什么游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不玩  是没有兴趣玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别弄了       -好了  坐好坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山田  别弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在曼谷上学的一名初中生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加强练习小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一位同学  佐伯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在4月13、14和15日迎来我们的新年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们叫它songkran
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在节日期间 人们...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种程度上不够胖的大腿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能称之为大腿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  叫小细腿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈奈子好球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺厉害的嘛 奈奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梳子借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺瘦的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里瘦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小岛你买了第八卷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 买回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很刺激吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  超级刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回借我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定要蹭上食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁蹭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薯片什么的  你饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  还有仙贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  下山的那个运动服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是在哪里买的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种微妙的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等...等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我君临碧霄  难解如狮身人面之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心比莹雪  如天鹅纯洁曼妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对移动线条的运动感到厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来不哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也从来不发笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  收卷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不是  是恋爱片嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  是恐怖片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:07:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  我肯定不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不了恐怖片的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  恐怖与欢乐的本质都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢  怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖和欢乐  本质都是惊奇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是  你肯定说书上就是这么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种小事是常识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖片有时候可能笑出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔界英豪什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  今天去小岛家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能看第八卷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈  去买冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个可乐味的好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我顺道去趟书店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又去书店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别总看那小黄书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的长相和名字还有出生地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座血型和职业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的江户时代的将军和喜欢的幕府时代的统领
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有喜欢的镰仓时代的掌权者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有布勒东的《田野的钥匙》吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也记得有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  不用买了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去给你找找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  高男
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要再盛一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天上了体育课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就站着了  排球课
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩他爸  还有点墨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我盛出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给可爱至极之人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽至极之人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照亮我心灵之人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如天使般纯洁之人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不朽的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬献我不灭的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她似韵味十足的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我生命中洋溢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又往我如饥似渴的心田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倾入无限的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这始终保鲜的香包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使我可爱的小屋散发芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一盏被人遗忘的香炉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透过黑夜升起一缕轻烟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高男　快去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛奶快点喝完
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不喝就要坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人又不喝牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算把数学弄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的大结局 看了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了看了  我都哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在发前几天数学测验的卷子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青木
