Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浦部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再稍微用点儿功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 春日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少分 考了多少分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要给你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 你看什么书呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这个汉字写错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是旧体字啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 快点还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你这类人怎么看也看不明白的书
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你说我是笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不还给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是啰嗦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 你知道波德莱尔么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事儿除了你没人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个 佐伯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐伯 98分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你非常努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈奈子 真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事儿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次也是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕啊 你在上补习班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 答应一声儿 你怎么不答应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看 倒数第一名 仲村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是0分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了名字啥也不写
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊你 将来走上社会了怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很烦哎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭虫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么跟老师说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说我是臭虫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学以后给我到办公室来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点过来啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个危险的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村 果然脑子与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得她有点吓人么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是搞不懂那家伙成天都在想些什么事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个朋友也没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有点让人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 也挺痛快的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是把下山气得抖个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是绝对不想和那样的女人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？ 你说什么呢 山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一副居高临下的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样也没有谁愿意和你交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日 照照你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有说别人的资格么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不是和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我读很多书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 又怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那脑子能理解得了么？ 文学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说交往对象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定选佐伯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说佐伯啊 下边毛很是旺盛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说女生的这种话 很没礼貌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 春日喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐伯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 原来是这样 哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书落在学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 要逃跑了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小岛这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说出侮辱佐伯同学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙怎么可能懂得欣赏佐伯同学的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:20:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢佐伯同学已经整整一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的缪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我生命中的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 佐伯同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概没有注意到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在读这类的书
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.47,0:23:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.74,0:23:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（春日君 总是在看书呢)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪恶的花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（不就是变态么？）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经无处可去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（春日君 我都看见了）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（一种强烈的色情感升了起来）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪恶的道路是如此的艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换  和我签下契约吧
